    .sheet-oracle-dice
      span {{payThePrice}}
    .sheet-oracle-table-text
      | {{#rollBetween() payThePrice 1 2}}
      span
        | Roll again and apply that result but make it worse. If you roll this result yet again, think of something dreadful that changes the course of your quest (
        em Ask the Oracle
        |  if unsure) and make it happen.
      | {{/rollBetween() payThePrice 1 2}}
      | {{#rollBetween() payThePrice 3 5}}
      span A person or community you trusted loses faith in you, or acts against you.
      | {{/rollBetween() payThePrice 3 5}}
      | {{#rollBetween() payThePrice 6 9}}
      span A person or community you care about is exposed to danger.
      | {{/rollBetween() payThePrice 6 9}}
      | {{#rollBetween() payThePrice 10 16}}
      span You are separated from something or someone.
      | {{/rollBetween() payThePrice 10 16}}
      | {{#rollBetween() payThePrice 17 23}}
      span Your action has an unintended effect.
      | {{/rollBetween() payThePrice 17 23}}
      | {{#rollBetween() payThePrice 24 32}}
      span Something of value is lost or destroyed.
      | {{/rollBetween() payThePrice 24 32}}
      | {{#rollBetween() payThePrice 33 41}}
      span The current situation worsens
      | {{/rollBetween() payThePrice 33 41}}
      | {{#rollBetween() payThePrice 42 50}}
