      | {{/rollBetween() payThePrice 51 59}}
      | {{#rollBetween() payThePrice 60 68}}
      span It is harmful.
      | {{/rollBetween() payThePrice 60 68}}
      | {{#rollBetween() payThePrice 69 77}}
