      | {{#rollBetween() endureStress 26 50}}
      span You give in to a fear or compulsion, and act against your better instincts.
      | {{/rollBetween() endureStress 26 50}}
      | {{#rollBetween() endureStress 51 100}}
      span You persevere.
      | {{/rollBetween() endureStress 51 100}}
  | {{/endureStress}}
